{"tid":959632,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔見電話] 偷電話死全家！","createTime":"2018-12-28T18:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T00:02:22.000Z","uid":228875,"like":0,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8660d14254da20297a65ba621b3e23deee3ac1","tid":959632,"uid":228875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"早兩日喺的士到唔見左電話<br />\n落車知道唔見已經用朋友電話不停打電話俾自己，打左百幾個電話，差唔多個幾鐘之後，部電話熄左機<br />\n一係就司機收工拎走左，一係就有乘客上車見到拎走左。因為落車嗰陣仲有50幾電無理由會咁快熄機<br />\n打過去的士報失熱線，都去左警署報失<br />\n知係自己on9無back up搞到啲野無哂，不過如果真係有人見到，麻煩俾返我因為入面有啲好重要嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b832e016475ee213b8768dc520b991c84cb04dc5","tid":959632,"uid":30578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f74d7ffbc04994fe649150e667c0a846556ee","tid":959632,"uid":75935,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"通常部電話都係有過左身既屋企人既合照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5420b4da2e43cfa294f3f598fdd7ffda076fe5","tid":959632,"uid":228875,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"其實我唔係好介意無左部電話<br />\n只係想拎返入面啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要肯俾返部電話我，我真係可以拎返啲資料之後俾返部電話你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bed8e51d1e62e165c404eda33968a937985149b","tid":959632,"uid":183417,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18